---
title: Easy Mediterranean Eggplant Soup with Crumbly Cheese & Toasted Almonds
description: Settle in for a cosy night with this hearty (and low-carb) roasted eggplant and cherry tomato soup.
Full of colourful veggies and classic Mediterranean flavours, the meal gets an extra boost with addictive
morsels of crumbled Greek-style cheese.

*This recipe is under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-mediterranean-eggplant-soup-d2d637c0.jpg
